The relationship between economic status and mortality of South Koreans, as it 
relates to average life expectancy.

Kim JM(1), Jo YS(2), Park EC(3), Cho WH(3), Choi J(4), Chang HS(5).

Author information:
(1)Department of Public Health, Graduate School, Yonsei University, Seoul, Korea 
Institute of Health Services Research, Yonsei University, Seoul, Korea National 
